uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor

Class DClassMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.hobo.model.motor.DClassMapper

  • public abstract class DClassMapper
extends java.lang.Object
    Generates a set of mappings between the Object Model (OM) classes (DObject-derived classes) from a set of one or more packages, plus any OM fields attached to those classes, and entities in one or more external sources.

    This is an abstract class whose concrete extensions will implement methods to generate external-identifiers for the classes and fields that are being mapped.
